    question: 'Shopify Email or Attentive for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Shopify Email when Shops wanting low-friction email inside Shopify Admin. Choose Attentive when Larger DTC brands with high SMS volume. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
